  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1. This project will build 3 no. 4-seater latrines for 1500 school children. 3 no. Rain Water Harvesting Tank to 3 deprived basic schools in Northern Ghana, which will serve 1500 children. It will ensure the formation and training of 3 School Health Clubs and the Provision of 18 Hand Washing with soap facilities in the selected schools. The project will also Sensitize 800 school girls on menstrual cycle management in the selected schools</narrative>
